## 🚀 Setup Instructions

### Prerequisites

| Tool | Version |
|------|---------|
| Java JDK | 17 or higher |
| Maven | 3.8+ |
| Microsoft SQL Server | 2019+ (or SQL Server Express) |
| MSSQL JDBC Driver | Resolved automatically via `pom.xml` |

---

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/faz2001/OceanViewResort.git
cd OceanViewResort
```

### 2. Set Up the Database

Run the schema script using SSMS or `sqlcmd`:

```bash
sqlcmd -S localhost -U sa -P yourPassword -i ovr/sql/schema.sql
```

### 3. Configure the Database Connection

Edit `src/main/java/com/hotel/db/DBConnection.java`:

```java
private static final String URL      = "jdbc:sqlserver://localhost:1433;databaseName=OceanViewResort";
private static final String USER     = "sa";
private static final String PASSWORD = "yourPassword";
```

### 4. Build with Maven

```bash
mvn clean package
```

### 5. Run the Server

```bash
mvn exec:java -Dexec.mainClass="com.hotel.Main"
```

### 6. Run Tests

```bash
mvn test
```

Test reports are generated in `target/surefire-reports/`.

### 7. Open in Browser

```
http://localhost:8080
```

