## 🔀 Git Workflow

This project used a **Feature Branch / Hotfix Workflow**. All changes were developed in dedicated branches and merged into `main` via pull requests. See [REPORT.md](./REPORT.md) for the full version control explanation.

### Branches Used

| Branch | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `main` | Stable, production-ready code |
| `master` | Initial development trunk |
| `feature/issue-1-health-endpoint` | Issue-tracked health-check feature |
| `feature/health-endpoint` | Health-check endpoint iteration |
| `hotfix/issue-2-db-error` | Urgent database error fix |

### Tags / Releases

```bash
git tag -a v1.0.0 -m "Initial stable release"
git tag -a v1.0.1 -m "Hotfix — database connection error resolved"
git push origin --tags
```

### GitHub Actions CI

Every push triggers two workflows:
1. **`java-ci.yml`** — Maven build and full test suite
2. **SLSA3 provenance** — Supply-chain security attestation

---

## 🧪 Tests

10 JUnit API integration test classes cover every major endpoint:

| Test Class | What It Tests |
|------------|--------------|
| `ApiSmokeTest` | Server starts and responds |
| `AuthApiTest` | Login and registration |
| `RoomsApiTest` | Room listing endpoints |
| `ReservationsApiTest` | Full reservation lifecycle |
| `BillingApiTest` | Billing record creation & retrieval |
| `EBillApiTest` | Electronic bill generation |
| `RatesApiTest` | Rate configuration endpoints |
| `StaffApiTest` | Staff management endpoints |
| `CorsOptionsTest` | CORS preflight responses |
| `NotFoundContractTest` | 404 contract for unknown routes |

